items.summary: Remove the 'Admin Setup' navigation link from the Navbar.tsx component at XPath /html[1]/body[1]/div[1]/div[1]/nav[1]/div[1]/div[2], ensuring no 'Admin Setup' or 'Register Admin' link appears in the navigation menu for any user (authenticated or unauthenticated, admin or non-admin), completely eliminating this navigation option from the menu bar

Verify that the admin registration functionality at route '/admin/register' remains accessible through direct URL navigation even though the navigation link is removed from the menu bar, ensuring admins can still register new admins by navigating directly to the URL when needed
